general.gigTitle: design and develop a responsive wordpress website

sellerCard.description:
I am a professional WordPress Developer serving happy clients around the world for the past 6 years with successfully completed 1000+ projects.                      
What I can do:
⇒ Design and Develop Responsive WP Websites (Personal, Blog, business wesbite, etc.),    ⇒ Convert Any PSD Template or sketch Into Wordpress Website,
⇒ On page SEO,
⇒ Creating New website in Wordpress from scratch,
⇒ Integrate any WP Plugins and Customise as needed,
⇒ Google analytics integration, 
⇒ Online booking system (Calendly) integration
⇒ Transfer, DNS Propagation & Securing the WP website and so on.

description.content:
Hi there,


I'm a professional web designer & developer with 7 years of experience working with international clients &agencies.


! IMPORTANT Note: Please contact me before purchasing a gig in order to make the buying process as efficient as possible.


Why choose me?


Ive been designing and developing WordPress websites for more than 7 years with 500+ completed projects. 

I have experience of large range projects including but not limited to blog sites, portfolio sites, agency, real-estate, business website and many more.


All packages will contain the following:

  • Clean, Elegant & Responsive Wordpress Web with Blog
  • RESPONSIVE Contact Form
  • Social Link Integration
  • Mailchimp integartion.
  • Security and Speed Optimized
  • SEO and Google Adwords friendly website.
  • Customized design from scratch
  • Customer Live Chat (tidio/messenger) integration 
  • Online booking system (calendly),
  • Easily Maintainable website

Please do not ask for any personal information, all communication must happen via Fiverr

No SEO - SMO INCLUDED. 

Domain and hosting must be provided by the buyer.

I do not provide e-commerce functionality or P. A .  Y.  M.  E.  N.  T. gateway in basic and standard packages.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide contents for the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I will upload the content to the website after creating the layout 
but I do not write content and I will require the contents (texts and images) from the website owner.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I edit my website and make changes by myself?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, you can make changes and work on the edits by yourself if you want. 
Wordpress is an easy-to-use and easily maintain CRM software for users. I can help with any questions relevant to this.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Domain and Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I am sorry my packages do not provide any domain and hosting service, I will need the website owner to provide me with a domain and hosting access to get started.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide e-commerce functionality?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide e-commerce functionality only, it is only included in my Premium gig.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide P. A. Y. M. E. N. T. Gateway functionality?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide P. A. Y. M. E. N. T. Gateway functionality in my Premium Gig only.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide SEO?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I do not provide any SEO or SMO services. But the site will be fully SEO friendly, 
I can integrate the SEO plugin ( Yoast) and also add the Keywords and meta data once you provide them.

reviews.comment: I came to Farjana with my own website that I tried to create. Needless to say, it did not go well, but thankfully Farjana was able to take my ideas and the work to date, and design a responsive and fluid website. She understood what I was trying to achieve and put her expertise to work. There were about 30 pages completed and it needed a couple of revisions to get it fully right, but it was also a big task, and she managed to finish it in about 10-12 days. Overall I couldn’t be happier and will definitely be coming back for more!

Farjana Soud truly impressed me with her exceptional attention to detail and professionalism, a beautiful and easy to navigate website that FAR EXCEEDED my expectations. I will be referring my friends - thank you Fajana, very much appreciated :)

seller_response.comment: Thanks Gwanita , i enjoyed working with you :)

reviews.comment: Farjana has been amazing! super responsive and quality work. I will continue to use her and her services. I highly recommend anyone reach out to her if you are looking for a website. Thanks so much Farjana! Keep up the great work.

Farjana Soud did an OUTSTANDING job! Her professionalism, attention to detail, and thorough documentation made the project seamless, and her deep understanding and cooperative attitude ensured a smooth collaboration. Highly recommend her for any website development needs 👏!
reliable and professional; will continue working with her
